Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Stops a func\_camera\_anim if it was playing an [MD5Anim](MD5ANIM_%28file_format%29 "MD5ANIM (file format)") file.

Usage
-----

*void* stop( )

Parameters
----------

None.

Examples
--------

    $mycamera.stop()

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.

